                University Library
              









Services





      View Menu
      
Down arrow icon












The Library’s primary goal is to provide quality services and resources for the support of our diverse community of users.
Please consult our full Service Policy for more information.





            Services Link Tiles
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            Accessibility Services
                    

                We welcome users with disabilities, and we commit to providing accessible services, spaces and resources for everyone.
            









                            Faculty Services
                    

                We support UIC faculty in teaching, research and publishing efforts, with our rich collections and many e-resources.
            









                            Visitor Services
                    

                All library locations are open to anyone, though some restrictions apply if you are not affiliated with UIC.
            









                            Course Reserves
                    

                Request or find course reserves for your class.
            









                            Digital Scholarship
                    

                The Digital Scholarship Hub amplifies digital scholarship for all on the UIC campus.
            









                            Request library instruction
                    

                Prepare students to find, evaluate and use information from library research tools.
            









                            Research Help
                    

                We help you get started, and help along the way.
            









                            Request items and Interlibrary Loan
                    

                Staff, students, faculty and emeritus faculty can request items from other libraries.
            









                            Distance Education Services
                    

                For distance education users and online students who connect remotely.
            









                            Reserve a study room
                    

                Study rooms are available at all libraries.
            









                            Reproduction Services
                    

                Special Collections can help to digitize or reproduce items from our collections
            












